        	   <span id="T1" class="TitleStartPos color-blueish MoveTitle">Consequences</span>
        	</h1>
          <div id="HorizontalRule" class="HR MoveHR"></div>
            <p id="p1" class="form-font-14 color-white OpacityZero MoveParagraph">The consequences of being a weak link are serious for you and our organization. Our organization could suffer significant financial losses due to fraud, network downtime, theft, or even extortion. Our reputation could be damaged and our trade secrets and intellectual property compromised. You could face disciplinary action and put your job at risk. And the organization or even <span class="text_bold-format color-blueish">you</span> could face civil or criminal penalties and fines.</p>
          </div>
      ]]></content>
